Appreciate your efforts SAM-DDR, but you are very confusing with your torrent titles, for example: this one says "DVD SCR" when it is from a cam source... 
your RASCALS torrent has "PDVDrip" which in nine years of torrent handling i have never come across before; what does it stand for?!? Preview-dvd maybe? (which would be a screener then anyway lol!), 
and also the "1CDrip" thing is a strange tag to use here, i can only assume that its maybe because you used to see some movie avi files supplied in two parts of around 700mb each in the olden days where VCD's were common place mainly because of the fact the files would fit on or came from cd's - so maybe your using that tag to show that this example is in one file??? 

Please don't think i'm slating you, your efforts are greatly appreciated as are all uploaders. It's just the title descriptions could cause confusion, and constuctive critiscm can lead to good things ;-)

Thankyou for uploading it, we look forward to seeing more from you.
